        "id": 5120
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-11-26T18:47:21Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "nit: if we can use DbModified time somehow, that would be better to avoid race conditions (e.g. process 1 updates task, process 2 updates task, process 2 sends pubsub message, process 1 sends pubsub message).",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 80,
        "startChar": 27,
