        "id": 5120
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-11-26T18:47:21Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Is it possible that this will deadlock? I.e. this sequence of calls:\n - stopTrackingModifiedData takes c.mtx\n - pubsub calls the callback passed to newSubscriber, which waits on c.mtx\n - stopTrackingModifiedData calls s.Stop -- is it possible there is a mutex here to ensure the callback finishes before the subscriber is stopped?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 118,
        "startChar": 11,
        "endLine": 118,
        "endChar": 19
      },
      "revId": "e7432b044c406b60b4c7e0b2a9131d0d82f1e000",
